<tr valign=top>
	<td colspan=2>
		<font face="Tahoma" size="+2" color="Blue">Presentation of Nominees to the Diocese</font><br>
		<font size="-1">The five nominees chosen by the Search and Nominating Committee will be presented to the diocese at five discussion sessions Oct. 22 through 25. Priority seating will be given to clergy and delegates to the Diocesan Convention. Other interested diocesan members are welcome to attend.</font>
	</td>
</tr>

<tr valign=top>
	<th align=left width=250><FONT FACE="Verdana" COLOR="Navy"><B>Date</B></FONT></th>
	<th align=left width=350><FONT FACE="Verdana" COLOR="Navy"><B>Location</B></FONT></th>
</tr>

<tr valign=top>
	<td>Thursday, Oct. 22<br>6:30 - 10:15 p.m.<br>Registration: 6:00 - 6:30 p.m.</td>
	<td>Trinity Church<br>425 Laurel Ave., Highland Park<br>(847) 432-6653</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td>Friday, Oct. 23<br>6:30 - 10:15 p.m.<br>Registration: 6:00 - 6:30 p.m.</td>
	<td>Church of the Transfiguration<br>12219 S. 86th Ave., Palos Park<br>(708) 448-1200</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td>Saturday, Oct. 24<br>12:30 - 4:15 p.m.<br>Registration: 12:00 - 12:30 p.m.</td>
	<td>Emmanuel Church<br>412 N. Church St., Rockford<br>(815) 964-5514</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td>Sunday, Oct. 25<br>2:00 - 5:45 p.m.<br>Registration: 1:30 - 2:00 p.m.</td>
	<td>St. Edmund's Church<br>6105  S. Michigan Ave., Chicago<br>(773) 288-0038</td>
</tr>
<tr valign=top>
	<td colspan=2><font size="-1">At each session, the clergy and delegates will be divided into groups of 50. Each group will be assigned a separate room for meeting with the nominees. Non-delegates will be assigned to groups as space allows. Because of time limitations, only clergy and lay delegates will be permitted to question the nominees.<br><br>
	Registrations for the presentation sessions must be submitted to the Search and Nominating Committee by Oct. 1. Registration forms are available through George Giles, Secretary, Search and Nominating Committee, 65 E. Huron St., Chicago, IL 60611.</font>
	</td>
</tr>

